data.description: Absolutely gorgeous two story traditional Bloomfield home located in Paloma Creek just minutes to the new PGA headquarters! Sweeping hardwood floors invite you inside this entertainers dream home. A formal dining room is located just off the entry way and is a wonderful place to enjoy family dinners. Make your way into the open concept living space with expansive sight-lines from the kitchen, family room and breakfast area. Prepare chef inspired meals in the fully equipped kitchen with granite counter-tops, gas cook-top, stainless steel appliances and under-mount lighting. Gather in the light filled family room highlighted by a wall of windows overlooking the spacious backyard and covered patio. The secluded primary bedroom is tucked in the back of the home and offers a luxurious en suite bath and walk-in closet. Desirable guest bedroom downstairs with full bath. Upstairs is a dream with a large game and media room. Excellent location close to Lake Lewisville.
